.TH "megaraid_reset_handler" 9 "megaraid_reset_handler" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
megaraid_reset_handler \- device reset handler for mailbox based driver
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" megaraid_reset_handler
.BI "(struct scsi_cmnd *scp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "scp" 12
reference command
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Reset handler for the mailbox based controller. First try to find out if
the FW is still live, in which case the outstanding commands counter mut go
down to 0. If that happens, also issue the reservation reset command to
relinquish (possible) reservations on the logical drives connected to this
host.
